high_descs: Turn right, move to the fridge, turn right, move forward, turn right to face the apple on the center island.
Pick up the apple on the island.
Turn right, head straight, then turn left to bring the apple to the sink.
Wash the apple in the sink.
Turn around, bring the cleaned apple to the microwave in the opposite corner of the room.
Put the cleaned apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned apple in the microwave.

high_descs: Go toward the refrigerator on your right, then turn right and go to face the kitchen island that is on your right.
Pick up the apple that is on the island countertop, near the bread.
Turn right and go back toward the fridge, then left to go to the sink, ahead and to your right.
Wash the apple in the sink and pick it up.
Turn to your right to face the opposite direction and go to the wall, then left to continue until you come to the microwave.
Put the apple into the microwave and leave it there.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean apple into a microwave.
